question: You are given an integer array coins representing coins of different denominations and an integer amount representing a total amount of money.
description: Return the fewest number of coins that you need to make up that amount. If that amount of money cannot be made up by any combination of the coins, return -1.

description: The test cases are generated so that the answer will fit in a 32-bit integer.
